This is the binary distribution of BACKside-IHO ROM.
Built from the inferiorhumanorgans repository for the Optimus V.
Thanks to Alex and all the rest of the IHO dev team,
as well as to AOSP, CyanogenMod, and all Optimus V devs!

Download to your sdcard
Download gapps to your sdcard
Boot into recovery
Wipe cache/dalvik cache
  (if comming from a non CM7 ROM,
   format boot, system, data, & cache)
Flash the BACKside-IHO zip file
Flash the gapps zip file
Reboot, be patient, profit!